Features

Easily add new tasks with descriptions.
Mark those tasks which have been completed to keep track of progress.
Display all tasks with clear indicators showing which tasks are complete or pending.
Error handling to ensure a smooth user experience.
Project Structure

'Task' class whichshows invidual tasks with attributes like descriptions and status.
'Main' class using 'public static void main(String[] args)' method. Initialized and user interactions are handled.
Requirement

Java SE 8** or later
